NEW DESIGN AND FEATURES! The Stormboard for iOS App has been completely rewritten with a sleek new look more features and increased functionality. On iPhone you ll find a clean streamlined interface that is more aligned with the Mac version. On iPad the app will work exactly the same way as it does on your Mac. We know our old version was limited in scope so we ve put all our efforts into creating a powerful and exciting new experience so that you and your team can work better together from anywhere!
Update AppStore listing Tour A few bug fixes

We ve spent lots of time under the hood . Loading Storms editing ideas and many other things should be much more snappy. New things: Full color and classic mode stickies. Log into the Storm on your PC to update these settings. Sticky note shapes! Assign sticky notes to people in your Storms as tasks. If you experience issues with our app please contact us:

Fixed: Whiteboards work much better Image thumbnails Storm loading improvements Other styling and stability issues. Previous Updates Keep up to date with the improved Activity tab Manage your tasks across all your storms If you experience issues with our app please contact us:
